&lt;p&gt;OneDegree is a next-generation insurtech company committed to revolutionizing the insurance industry through design and digital innovation. Our mission is to set a new customer-first standard for insurance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As one of the first virtual insurance companies licensed by the Hong Kong Insurance Authority, we specialize in providing insurance products through online channels. We take pride in delivering innovative products and services via digital platforms. Currently, we offer pet insurance, fire insurance, critical illness insurance, and home insurance, with plans to expand our coverage options in the coming year.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are seeking a motivated and talented iOS App developer to join our team. This is an excellent opportunity to gain hands-on experience in a dynamic and fast-paced work environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will have the opportunity to learn about the development and operational models of online insurance products, and actively participate in the creation of conceptual products, gaining valuable insights into software engineering and cross-functional collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
