&lt;li&gt;Ensure the performance, quality, and responsiveness of applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage code versioning using Git and participate in code reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and fix bugs and performance bottlenecks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the deployment process and submission to the App Store&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide input on UI/UX design improvements and future product direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the development of a Proof of Concept (POC) for a new insurance service, including implementing select features using Flutter for cross-platform evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
