&lt;li&gt;Provide support to various departments, including Customer service, Claims, Policy Administration, and Product/Project Management. Facilitate communication and collaboration to ensure smooth operations and achieve company goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle assigned tasks and ad-hoc duties as required. Support management in coordinating team efforts, streamlining processes, and maintaining efficient operations.&lt;/li&gt;
