&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Feedback &amp;amp; Engineering Feed-Forward:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate closely with the engineering team to improve reliability and operational efficiency. Translate real-world pain points, extreme edge cases, client feedback, and performance bottlenecks encountered on the

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OneDegree &lt;/strong&gt;is an InsurTech company, with a virtual insurer license granted by the Hong Kong Insurance Authority in 2020 Since then, we have grown quickly into the leading Hong Kong virtual insurer with an ambition to bring consumers a seamless and instant insurance and claim experience through technology. We currently offer multi-line digital insurance products, including pet, medical, fire and home insurance for individuals, and cyber security and digital asset insurance for enterprise businesses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to join us and make a change? We are looking for a senior Marketing Manager/&amp;nbsp;Marketing Manager in winning the market and expanding our market shares!&lt;/p&gt;
